## Future direction

This rubric is a single document. As the project grows, plausible next steps:

- Specialized rubrics for sub-domains under `docs/rubric/` if categories diverge significantly
- Per-PR template that references rubric items by ID
- Adapt the section list to your project's actual concerns: drop, add, reword as you learn
